graph LR
    subgraph Frontend ["Frontend (Browser/Client)"]
        UI[User Interface]
        Logic[JS Logic]
    end

    subgraph Backend ["Backend (Server/Cloud)"]
        API[Hono API]
        DB[(Cloud Firestore)]
    end

    UI -->|Interaction| Logic
    Logic -->|HTTP Request| API
    API -->|Read/Write| DB
    API -->|HTTP Response (JSON)| Logic
    Logic -->|Update UI| UI

    style Frontend fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#01579b
    style Backend fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#e65100
    style DB fill:#f1f8e9,stroke:#33691e
